itemDescription: Olympic lacrosse player of Great Britain

wikipedia_page.main: Hubert Walter Ramsey (3 October 1874 – 8 February 1968) was a British lacrosse player who competed in the 1908 Summer Olympics. He was part of the British team which won the silver medal.
